column5: Checkout our weekly update video for weather and whats happening. We will have fishing reports from the first groups next week! /https://canadianflyinfishing.ca/week...r-may-20-2019/

I've been fishing Little V beginning last Friday. Late cold water seems to have big pike guessing. I'm finding warm water shallow bays, but not enough pike are finding the same bays. Bite is improving fast. One of those times when we should have been here NEXT WEEK. Missed only 1 opener on same lake, with streak beginning 3rd Saturday, May, 1984.
Brett is a little grumpy since he had materials in camp for new dock. Late ice prohibited work. Looks like a lumber yard out front.
